Resveratrol is a naturally occurring antioxidant, and it boasts a variety of health-preserving benefits for dogs. As a powerful antioxidant, Resveratrol targets free radicals, reducing oxidative stress and supporting cognitive health. And that’s not all; it also helps to promote cardiovascular and joint health, as well as maintaining energy levels in aging dogs.
Vitamin E is essential for a dog’s overall health and well-being. Like Resveratrol, it also targets Free Radicals while also supporting immune system function and silky, shiny coats!
Vital vitamins needed to help maintain natural defenses.
